OL,3,CThree family members found dead in home
OL,5,FPolice are investigating the
OL,6,Fcircumstances after three people were
OL,7,Ffound dead in a home in Ballymena.
OL,9,FThe discovery was made in the Old
OL,10,FCullybackey Road area on Monday
OL,11,Fmorning.
OL,13,FThe three people were related and
OL,14,Ffound inside the family home, police
OL,15,Fsaid.
OL,17,F"There is no ongoing risk to the
OL,18,Fpublic," police said in a statement.
OL,20,F"A further update will follow in due
OL,21,Fcourse."
